<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <title>Booking Completed - Please Leave a Review</title>
  </head>
  <body>
      <h1>Thank you for staying at <%= booking.couch.user.first_name.capitalize %>'s Place</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= booking.user.first_name.capitalize %>,</p>
      <p>We love to see that your booking with <%= booking.user.first_name.capitalize %> has been successfully completed. We hope you had a great experience staying at their place.</p>
      <p>We encourage you to leave a review for <%= booking.user.first_name.capitalize %> on their profile to help other guests make informed decisions about staying with them in the future.</p>
      <p>Leaving a review is quick and easy. Simply follow the link below and share your honest thoughts about your stay with <%= booking.user.first_name.capitalize %>.</p>
      <p><%= link_to 'Leave a Review', new_guest_review_path(@booking.host, @booking) %></p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing to stay with <%= booking.user.first_name.capitalize %>. We hope to welcome you back soon.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>your Quouch Team</p>
  </body>
</html>